stimulus:
We will now start the practice for the experiment.

For these trials, you must press the left key or the right key depending on the shape of the stimulus. Make sure to respond as quickly and accurately as possible to the shape.

The responses for each shape are as follows:

  • circle: left key
  • triangle: left key
  • rhombus: right key
  • pentagon: right key

Remember these rules before you proceed.

Press enter to begin.
We will now start with a practice session. In this practice concentrate on responding quickly and accurately to each stimuli.

Please take this time to read your feedback and to take a short break! Press enter to continue

Average reaction time: 508 ms. Accuracy: 98%

Done with this practice.

We will now start the second practice for the experiment.

On some trials a star will appear around the shape. If a star appears, please change your response from the left key or right key, to the Z key.

Do not wait to see if a star will appear before you make your response. Please continue to respond to each shape as quickly and as accurately as possible.

Remember these rules before you proceed.

  • circle: left key
  • triangle: left key
  • rhombus: right key
  • pentagon: right key

If a star appears, the correct response on that trial is the Z key.

Press enter to begin.
